text: Margarita Gasparyan and Andrea Hlaváčková were the defending champions, but Gasparyan chose not to participate this year and Hlaváčková chose to compete in Rabat instead. Anna-Lena Grönefeld and Květa Peschke won the title, defeating Lucie Hradecká and Kateřina Siniaková in the final, 6–4, 7–6(7–3). ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== == References == * Main draw Doubles
